messages.content:
Content views and engagement really depends a lot on context. 

If you keep making good content, you will get trust and brings you customers in long term. 

We get some high intent leads for a particular land video but the most of the times its very unreliable and not enough to make any transaction. You always need to have more reliable sources to get leads
It would be very helpful if you reply
I am starting real estate broking in Maharashtra so I want to get an idea how many customers can we get through Instagram
How many customers do you get from Instagram who actually pay to buy the land
